      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "In master, the data directory can be configured on first startup (or when it's missing, or when bitcoin-qt.exe is started with `-choosedatadir`). This is stored in the registry.\nSo there is no reason anymore to provide it in the startup .lnk command line.\nAll other options can be set in the bitcoin.conf.\n",
